OL,6,CG2009FUKTV Style is rebranded Home.
OL,7,FThe channel's schedule is repositioned
OL,8,Fto focus on home improvement/lifestyle
OL,9,Fand gardening. In 2019, the BBC's stake
OL,10,Fin the channel was bought by UKTV
OL,11,Fco-owner Discovery Inc - the channel
OL,12,Fwas consequently rebranded HGTV on 21st
OL,13,FJanuary 2020.
